{"id":208292,"date":[{"year":1950,"month":12,"day":18}],"page":"6","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"文学界","column":"","genre":"","count":"614","ytitle":"","mtitle":"我们到朝鲜去!","ftitle":"——给医务工作者","authors":["罗飞"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"罗飞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(一)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了兄弟的朝鲜!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了花繁叶茂的祖国!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了白鸽飞翔的全人类的和平!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同志们，我们到朝鲜去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到保卫祖国的最前线"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到保卫和平的最前线"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朝鲜去!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(二)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和平是我们期望!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了和平"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中朝人民不屈地举起枪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枪，在战士底手上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和平，在我们底心上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"装备起医疗器械药品和行囊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白求恩的血液"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在毛泽东的医务工作者"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胸中腾荡……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(三)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白血球的增加"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是为了抵抗细菌的侵袭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"守卫美好的日子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"守卫密汁的果实"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"守卫太阳普照的祖国"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"医务工作者"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们也都应该是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民中国的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白血球"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(四)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国强盗的枪弹射向朝鲜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国强盗的炮弹轰向朝鲜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国强盗的炸弹掷向朝鲜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"……还梦想射向我们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轰向我们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"掷向我们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们朝鲜的兄弟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已经在流血……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们底血亲的兄弟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了制止世界的流血"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而流血"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了制止世界的流血"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们底兄弟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用他们底枪弹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了医治流血的兄弟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们——医务工作者"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"义不容辞的献出"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们底技术绷带和止血钳……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(五)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"成千封的电报涌向白宫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抱着孩子的妇女赶向成功湖……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要求和平"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带着红十字旗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带着配尼西林"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带着伤包"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"管血钳和鑷子……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到朝鲜去!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到朝鲜去!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"隔着遥远的海洋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们为了和平的心灵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是相联的!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(六)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鸭绿江流过"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国和朝鲜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中朝人民的苦难相连"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中朝人民的血海也曾流在一起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们解放了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们胜利了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好兄弟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们没有忘记"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当今天强盗欺凌你们的时候"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们来了!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们来了!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带枪的同志"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"协助你们驱除"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国的野兽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东的医务工作者"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将供献出"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们底所有"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了朝鲜灿烂的未来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了人类灿烂的未来……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好兄弟:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们来了!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九五○、十二、一○、上海"}]}